Section 129: 129. (1) A data user shall not transfer any personal data of a data subject to a place outside Malaysia unless to such place as specified by the Minister, upon the recommendation of the Commissioner, by notification published in the Gazette.

(2) For the purposes of subsection (1), the Minister may specify any place outside Malaysia if—
